PROTECTS YOU EVERYWHERE


FSP FACTORY SPECIFICATION PARTS

Your Kenmore deserves the best. That is why Sears provides top quality parts to back up Sears factory trained technicians who service the product.

The way to save money on service is to prevent costly call backs caused by failure of inferior replacement parts or service. Remember . . . the difference in cost between the genuine replacement part and a non-genuine part and Sears quality service compared with unknown service seldom amounts to more than "pennies". You gamble on a parts failure and a service call back when you use anything but Sears parts and Sears quality service.

Sears parts are made to the original specifications to fit right . . . function better . . . last longer. Remember . . . when your Kenmore needs service to specify Sears service which provides:
- Prompt service whenever you need if.
- Expert service by factory trained technicians.
- Guaranteed Faciory Specification Paris especially made for your Kenmore.

SEARS SERVICE AND PARTS ARE BEST FOR SEARS PRODUCTS

SERVICE BEYOND GUARANTEE PERIOD
Your new KENMORE Appliance carries a most liberal service and parts guarantee. However, major appliances are just like cars and service will probably be needed beyond the guarantee period to keep your appliance operating at top efficiency. You can be sure your KENMORE will always operate at top efficiency if you have a KENMORE Service Contract which is available at a small additional charge now, or may be purchased at any time during the regular guarantee period - . - - this contract assures you of
- Prompt service whenever you need it
- Expert service by factory - trained technicians
- Guaranteed SEARS parts especially made for your machine
- No sudden repair expenses
For additional information about this "Pennies per day" plan, ask the salesman, any SEARS serviceman, Customer Service, or Credit person.
